                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>Augusta</placeName>\n                <date>Nove 29<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> 1851</date>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <addressee>Rev I Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">My Dear Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">enclosed<lb/> you find an order on <persName>Mayer Haas</persName>\n                &amp;c<lb/> for forty two 24/100 Doll a part of <sic>colections</sic><lb/> that I\n                have made for you as follows<lb/>\n                <persName>Mess Caro</persName> &amp; <persName>Blascoer</persName> for 2 sets of\n                the<lb/> five book <persName>moses</persName> 15 30.00</p>\n            <p>2 fine prayer books sent to my</p>\n            <table cols=\"3\" rows=\"5\">\n                <row>\n                    <cell>order</cell>\n                    <cell>5</cell>\n                    <cell>10.00</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>one prayer book “</cell>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell>\n                        <hi rend=\"underline\"> 2.50</hi>\n                    </cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell>42.50</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell>\n                        <hi rend=\"underline\"> 21</hi>\n                    </cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>paid ½ 00 exchange</cell>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell>$42.29</cell>\n                </row>\n            </table>\n            <p>for above please acknowledge reced<lb/>\n                <persName>Mr Morritz Schwarz</persName> has also subscribed<lb/> for one year to\n                your <sic>Occitend</sic> you<lb/> will please forward the same to<lb/>\n                <persName>M Schwarz</persName>\n                <placeName>Augusta Ga</placeName></p>\n            <p><persName>Mr M Jacobs</persName> of <placeName>Athens</placeName> made complaint\n                to<lb/> me in regard that he has received but<lb/> 2 No of his <sic>Occidtent</sic>\n                &amp; has subscribed<lb/> at the time when you were in our<lb/> city last news we\n                have but little our<lb/> congregation is coming on slow although<lb/> our\n                    <add>Hebrew</add>\n                <persName>Mr I Schatz</persName> is well beliked &amp;<lb/> fully deserves it, He is\n                a gentleman that<lb/> haves<add>?</add> a good <sic>caracter</sic> but he is not</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3348h289/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
