                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>able to <sic>Legtur</sic> which is very much<lb/> wanting in a place like ours. I\n                have<lb/> a great trouble to get <add>Hebrew</add> on <date><sic>Sabath</sic></date>\n                &amp;<lb/> the fact is if they should not improve<lb/> in a short time in religious\n                feeling<lb/> I fear nothing will remain but the<lb/> name. My intention is to move\n                to<lb/> your city next fall, where I hope<lb/> to hear your valuable\n                    <sic>Legtures</sic> on<lb/> many occasion. I do it also more<lb/> on account of\n                my children as I<lb/> wish to <sic>rase</sic> them like Jews, I am<lb/> satisfied in\n                our place, there never<lb/> will be done anything to our children<lb/> please let me\n                hear from you soon<lb/>\n                <persName>Mrs Mayer</persName> sends her best respects<lb/> to you also\n                    <persName>Mrs Lambert</persName>.<lb/> and accept the same from your<lb/> most\n                truly</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(6)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Isaac Mayer</persName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3348h289/canvas/p2"
